00:23:33.810 --> 00:23:36.920 align:middle line:84%
Another study, virtual reality,
has been around long enough.

00:23:36.920 --> 00:23:39.440 align:middle line:84%
Psychology Today
published an article,

00:23:39.440 --> 00:23:42.007 align:middle line:84%
young children-- so for
example, three years old,

00:23:42.007 --> 00:23:43.840 align:middle line:84%
