physically, because they're not

00:24:01.960 --> 00:24:03.020 align:middle line:10%
using them, obviously.

00:24:03.020 --> 00:24:03.400 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Atrophying.

00:24:03.400 --> 00:24:05.400 align:middle line:84%
>> BRADEN: Compared to
other children their age,

00:24:05.400 --> 00:24:08.840 align:middle line:84%
