00:35:59.060 --> 00:36:02.350 align:middle line:84%
and you're going to choose how
we start interfacing with this

00:36:02.350 --> 00:36:05.620 align:middle line:84%
stuff, because that is going to
begin very rapidly atrophying

00:36:05.620 --> 00:36:06.910 align:middle line:90%
the creative capabilities.

00:36:06.910 --> 00:36:08.368 align:middle line:84%
>> BRADEN: Well,
you just asked me,

00:36:08.368 --> 00:36:09.850 align:middle line:84%
if I were president
of the world,

00:36:09.850 --> 00:36:12.350 align:middle line:84%
first thing I would do is, I
would bring these world leaders

00:36:12.350 --> 00:36:16.280 align:middle line:84%
together, with no armies
and no technology in a room,

00:36:16.280 --> 00:36:19.420 align:middle line:84%
to look one another in the eyes
and talk about our children

00:36:19.420 --> 00:36:21.770 align:middle line:84%
and say whatever time we
have left in this world,

00:36:21.770 --> 00:36:23.210 align:middle line:90%
how much good can we do?

00:36:23.210 --> 00:36:27.730 align:middle line:10%
How far can we take this world
and the people that trust

00:36:27.730 --> 00:36:29.270 align:middle line:10%
us enough to put us in power?

00:36:29.270 --> 00:36:30.687 align:middle line:10%
That's the first
thing I would do.

00:36:30.687 --> 00:36:33.330 align:middle line:10%
When it comes to the
technology, it's not

00:36:33.330 --> 00:36:34.750 align:middle line:10%
right or wrong, good or bad.

00:36:34.750 --> 00:36:37.860 align:middle line:84%
We are learning to
allow the technology

00:36:37.860 --> 00:36:40.620 align:middle line:84%
to serve us rather
than enslave us.

00:36:40.620 --> 00:36:42.390 align:middle line:84%
And what's happening
is the technology

00:36:42.390 --> 00:36:47.400 align:middle line:84%
has advanced faster than the
morality of how we implement it

00:36:47.400 --> 00:36:48.460 align:middle line:90%
in our lives.

00:36:48.460 --> 00:36:49.960 align:middle line:84%
So we're playing a
game of catch up.

00:36:49.960 --> 00:36:51.335 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: So
where do you start?

00:36:51.335 --> 00:36:53.050 align:middle line:84%
Average household,
You've got kids.

00:36:53.050 --> 00:36:54.092 align:middle line:90%
They're on their devices.

00:36:54.092 --> 00:36:55.925 align:middle line:84%
Now, you know they know
they don't even have

00:36:55.925 --> 00:36:57.160 align:middle line:90%
to do their homework anymore.

00:36:57.160 --> 00:36:58.630 align:middle line:84%
